# Netlify Redirects File
# This file handles the Single Page Application (SPA) routing 
# and proxies API requests to the backend server on Render.

# 1. Proxy API requests to Render backend
# REPLACE the URL below with your actual Render backend URL once deployed
/api/*  https://YOUR-BACKEND-URL.onrender.com/api/:splat  200

# 2. Redirect all other routes to index.html for React Router
/*      /index.html  200
